A framework intended to assist in the development of .Net framework web application.
summary:
This package contains dlls offering assistance building line of business apps by providing functionality addressing cross-cutting concerns, generic standard contract wcf services, restful webapi infrastructure, and data access support to several datastores.

The xf provides a generic standard contract service wherein a client simply makes a RESTful type call for any dto or business object, and the data access code is discovered and executed at runtime using MEF.  

The xf also includes three dlls to assist in building a robust RESTful webapi, where each api call may be logged (along with what code responded to the call).  Route handling controllers may be implemented as discoverable dlls, so that deployment may consist of simply adding dlls to a folder.

UrhoSharp is a lightweight Game Engine suitable for using with C# and F# to create games that run on Android, iOS, Mac, Windows and Unix. The game engine is available as a portable class library, allowing your game code to be written once and shared across all platforms. UrhoSharp is powered by Urho3D (http://urho3d.github.io/), a game engine that has been under development for more than a decade.   All the samples from Urho3D have been ported to C# to help you get started: https://github.com/xamarin/urho-samples

description: UrhoSharp is a lightweight Game Engine suitable for using with C# and F# to create games that run on Android, iOS, Mac, Windows and Unix. The game engine is available as a portable class library, allowing your game code to be written once and shared across all platforms. UrhoSharp is powered by Urho3D (http://urho3d.github.io/), a game engine that has been under development for more than a decade.   All the samples from Urho3D have been ported to C# to help you get started: https://github.com/xamarin/urho-samples
summary: Cross Platform, 2D and 3D Game Engine for C# (Android, iOS, Windows, Mac).
